						<p>Slab lying in a field out side the village.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">9th-10th century A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>It records the death of Bhima-tuṟuvaḷḷa, son of Sīya tuṟuvaḷḷa in a cattle raid. It is in characters of the 9th-10th century A.D.</p>						

